        Convenience constructor, which calls the super-constructor and disables the action.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the JosmAction, as displayed in the menu
        tooltip - a longer description of the JosmAction, that is displayed as tooltip
        shortcutId - an ID for the Shortcut as described in Shortcut.registerShortcut(String, String, int, int) (the passage about the second parameter)
        shortcutName - a name for the shortcut (displayed to the user, so use a self-explanatory and translated String). See the description of the second parameter in Shortcut.registerShortcut(String, String, int, int)
        toolbarId - identifier for the toolbar preferences
        See Also:
        JosmAction.JosmAction(String, String, String, Shortcut, boolean, String, boolean), Shortcut.registerShortcut(String, String, int, int)
